Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.80,0:00:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看見痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.04,0:00:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是空虛地渡過每一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.38,0:00:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在充滿消沉心情的城市裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.96,0:00:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在優美地閃耀着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NCarry On！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.76,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要灰心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NShinin Oh！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.87,0:00:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被破壞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.14,0:00:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成愛啊，\N像把宇宙包裏一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.08,0:01:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.59,0:01:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.47,0:01:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏的殘餘部隊向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前去\N卡沙尼里亞的胡索等人進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己\N實力的胡索陷於苦戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有V2的光之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索就會大量殺戮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而須要自我反省了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡沙尼里亞得到一晚的寧靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超高空攻擊之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那麽興奮會吵醒大家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聼到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.71,0:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索你也聼到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都聼到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在天空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有甚麽事呀！ 真吵耳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.55,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聼到鈴聲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼聼得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，要出發去拉京基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們放心去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森林中的空氣有點不同吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我稍為習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的爸爸去了湖那邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聼說找到看來能居住的小屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索去了拉京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要去取令白色方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛上宇宙的噴射器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽？\N和我們留在這裡就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去工作比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他會胡思亂想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差少少，慢慢來，太快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪斯先生，由加小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查拜託你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅美洛先生，\N真的要上宇宙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏只是用\N停戰協定拖延時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而聯邦軍就用來作為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽也不做的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想由那個大叔來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不可以說出真正的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他現在的意見是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊的接續完成了吧？\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危險吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了！   走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個女仔！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裡！   快滾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人殺死爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是叔叔他們說的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪斯，這邊也要快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的爸爸是個軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用石擲別人是很羞恥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.40,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會令爸爸的英名…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我戰鬥了，對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是遊擊隊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩不可以參加戰爭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不用你同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再幫遊擊隊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地球耕田種菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也不要住在基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.79,0:05:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然想那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.93,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的事我們自己會決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.17,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，你做甚麽？快來幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪露天娜小姐她們已睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼未睡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他會哭到倦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所…在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過廁所在這邊吧，蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為心臟已停頓了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去\N電腦資料庫那裡做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想調查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麽晚查資料？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是譯解字典的鈴網目呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事呀？\N你聼到那種聲音嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,執行斷頭台刑罰的人上街時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會把鈴掛在腰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前有那樣的習慣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請開始，瑪貝德小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，為了測試噴射器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們飛去卡沙尼里亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基地居住區的方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷射砲好像從\N正上方射下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.03,0:07:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽回事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏的人也在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯不能出發嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎已點火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！ 你去哪裡！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來！ 又會有攻擊來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯說他們能避開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索沒回音，他去了哪裡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在哪裡呀！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種雷射砲的威力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從很高的地方射來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縮低你們的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會有甚麽飛來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事呢，沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你！ ？為什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭，\N我帶你們去安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶路，行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在被擊中前出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.13,0:08:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時不用問我！ 立即出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器庫的方向好像被擊中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上這艘船逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上這艘船！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.79,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐，我是胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在回來白色方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要上遊擊隊的船逃離基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點，胡索回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發 知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯也已裝上噴射器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也進行噴射器的測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲變得利害了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉京的方向好像有空襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不大清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索的無線電機真古老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神聖軍事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有從高空\N攻擊拉京的武器嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.41,0:09:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是卑斯柏\N破壞停戰協定嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否卑斯柏，那就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，到達卡沙尼里亞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，要降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝着噴射器飛到這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了甚麽事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊，奧迪羅，上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是瑪貝德小姐你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由加也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士準備出發 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索你也準備V2 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出擊前\N我有個地方要帶你們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們在這裡等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅已在機裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.89,0:10:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部白色機動戰士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這班小孩在操縱的！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V1也要出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個小孩是機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他所說的完全有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.65,0:11:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請上來，我帶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.20,0:11:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你…丈夫的墳墓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送莉娜女仕去到後\N就回來會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利害！   下面很黑呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是墳墓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由面前數超第九個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個親切的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已告訴\N我們爸爸的墳墓所在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的墳墓！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他殺死爸爸的！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死爸爸的人沒理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會告訴\N我們爸爸的墳墓所在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以那麽簡單\N就當別人是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！   媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後爸爸會在天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.84,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.71,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸會不高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大家的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥捷！ ！ 為甚麽！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，你在裡面吧，胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我明白你很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向都很小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些鈴聲令我有不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聼聞執行死刑的人上街時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.57,0:14:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會把鈴掛在腰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在贊斯卡羅的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聼聞花娜.潔芳的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她以前是拉京基地的司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是使用斷頭台的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，\N莎蒂，她們拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒勒隊還未追上來嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦是雷射砲的目標吧！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才要逃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長！ 把連賀斯垂直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盾牌向上吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很難平行能量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們由上空攻擊我們啊！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟正在上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.77,0:15:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有飛行物體在成層圈，\N只得一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位置呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在正上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是戰艦，也不是機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉去螢光幕 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.39,0:16:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲不斷接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日由我指揮，沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然，由加小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要讓瑪貝德使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.57,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟的大砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在敵人的目標是連賀斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拖延時間讓連賀斯逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很消極吧！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要查清楚敵人的身份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入射程距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米加粒子砲準備發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉斯達也要出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很頭痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.66,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴在響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.78,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由下面攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面也有防護罩嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是失去頭部！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肩部的新月是弱點嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種地方也有雷射砲嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然被敵人瞄準我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德她們\N不是在掩護我們嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅，讓瑪貝德使用大砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！不將他擊落的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡也攻不入去嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由加小姐！ 你去得太前了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從它的飛行性能看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是從宇宙飛下來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的機動戰士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.26,0:18:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何米加粒子砲也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好頭痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跌下去呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德！ 有甚麽事！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝入來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我未輸的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.39,0:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是這種技倆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在飛走！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部機後退了！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？奧迪羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制系統沒受到損壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是更換頭部就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我們立即飛上宇宙！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏開始正式行動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡有傷者！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉斯達的頭部也需要更換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.66,0:19:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在停戰協定期間，卑斯柏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們\N和那種敵人剛交過手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會上宇宙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們在卡沙尼里亞啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請給我們少許時間！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.51,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很想批准你們，但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是為\N親愛的故鄉而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們須要時間向故鄉道別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是感情用事的時候嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊斯卡羅的卑斯柏已…！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧！ 我們也要補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一日吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.83,0:20:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.67,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們去吧，一定要回來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要保重呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要保重呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不見艾莉莎小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的身體還是不舒服嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！ 不用這樣做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！\N你們要整理好我們的家呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房也要整理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是在卡沙尼里亞那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會合了嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起戰爭，\N這種事沒大不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聼說你媽媽已過身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.85,0:21:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.53,0:21:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴了我們一處好地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖的對面有座小山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.48,0:21:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，我要失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索上來了，瑪貝德艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.86,0:21:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向卡沙尼里亞道別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在銀色的海上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.24,0:22:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灼熱的波浪湧上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.05,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到跪下的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.92,0:22:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變成說話，\N只是你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.50,0:23:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能變得優美就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.37,0:23:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次TENDERNESS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.51,0:23:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的内心在月亮的菱鏡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.14,0:23:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着閃耀的未來在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.15,0:23:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次和你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.79,0:23:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你的瞳孔顯出孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.20,0:23:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上到宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.27,0:23:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待我們的是擁有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.03,0:23:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕雷射砲的\N機動戰士和鈴聲
